37#define KEX_COOKIE_LEN 16
38
39#define KEX_DH1 "diffie-hellman-group1-sha1"
40#define KEX_DH14_SHA1 "diffie-hellman-group14-sha1"
41#define KEX_DH14_SHA256 "diffie-hellman-group14-sha256"
42#define KEX_DH16_SHA512 "diffie-hellman-group16-sha512"
43#define KEX_DH18_SHA512 "diffie-hellman-group18-sha512"
44#define KEX_DHGEX_SHA1 "diffie-hellman-group-exchange-sha1"
45#define KEX_DHGEX_SHA256 "diffie-hellman-group-exchange-sha256"
46#define KEX_ECDH_SHA2_NISTP256 "ecdh-sha2-nistp256"
47#define KEX_ECDH_SHA2_NISTP384 "ecdh-sha2-nistp384"
48#define KEX_ECDH_SHA2_NISTP521 "ecdh-sha2-nistp521"
49#define KEX_CURVE25519_SHA256 "curve25519-sha256"
50#define KEX_CURVE25519_SHA256_OLD "curve25519-sha256@libssh.org"
51#define KEX_SNTRUP4591761X25519_SHA512 "sntrup4591761x25519-sha512@tinyssh.org"
52
53#define COMP_NONE 0
54/* pre-auth compression (COMP_ZLIB) is only supported in the client */
55#define COMP_ZLIB 1
56#define COMP_DELAYED 2
57
58#define CURVE25519_SIZE 32
59
60enum kex_init_proposals {
61 PROPOSAL_KEX_ALGS,
62 PROPOSAL_SERVER_HOST_KEY_ALGS,
63 PROPOSAL_ENC_ALGS_CTOS,
64 PROPOSAL_ENC_ALGS_STOC,
65 PROPOSAL_MAC_ALGS_CTOS,
66 PROPOSAL_MAC_ALGS_STOC,
67 PROPOSAL_COMP_ALGS_CTOS,
68 PROPOSAL_COMP_ALGS_STOC,
69 PROPOSAL_LANG_CTOS,
70 PROPOSAL_LANG_STOC,
71 PROPOSAL_MAX
72};
73
74enum kex_modes {
75 MODE_IN,
76 MODE_OUT,
77 MODE_MAX
78};
79
80enum kex_exchange {
81 KEX_DH_GRP1_SHA1,
82 KEX_DH_GRP14_SHA1,
83 KEX_DH_GRP14_SHA256,
84 KEX_DH_GRP16_SHA512,
85 KEX_DH_GRP18_SHA512,
86 KEX_DH_GEX_SHA1,
87 KEX_DH_GEX_SHA256,
88 KEX_ECDH_SHA2,
89 KEX_C25519_SHA256,
90 KEX_KEM_SNTRUP4591761X25519_SHA512,
91 KEX_MAX
92};

94#define KEX_INIT_SENT 0x0001
95#define KEX_INITIAL 0x0002
96
97struct sshenc {
98 char *name;
99 const struct sshcipher *cipher;
100 int enabled;
101 u_int key_len;
102 u_int iv_len;
103 u_int block_size;
104 u_char *key;
105 u_char *iv;
106};
107struct sshcomp {
108 u_int type;
109 int enabled;
110 char *name;
111};
112struct newkeys {
113 struct sshenc enc;
114 struct sshmac mac;
115 struct sshcomp comp;
116};
117
118struct ssh;
119
120struct kex {
121 u_char *session_id;
122 size_t session_id_len;
123 struct newkeys *newkeys[MODE_MAX];
124 u_int we_need;
125 u_int dh_need;
126 int server;
127 char *name;
128 char *hostkey_alg;
129 int hostkey_type;
130 int hostkey_nid;
131 u_int kex_type;
132 char *server_sig_algs;
133 int ext_info_c;
134 struct sshbuf *my;
135 struct sshbuf *peer;
136 struct sshbuf *client_version;
137 struct sshbuf *server_version;
138 sig_atomic_t done;
139 u_int flags;
140 int hash_alg;
141 int ec_nid;
142 char *failed_choice;
143 int (*verify_host_key)(struct sshkey *, struct ssh *);
144 struct sshkey *(*load_host_public_key)(int, int, struct ssh *);
145 struct sshkey *(*load_host_private_key)(int, int, struct ssh *);
146 int (*host_key_index)(struct sshkey *, int, struct ssh *);
147 int (*sign)(struct ssh *, struct sshkey *, struct sshkey *,
148 u_char **, size_t *, const u_char *, size_t, const char *);
149 int (*kex[KEX_MAX])(struct ssh *);
150 /* kex specific state */
151 DH *dh; /* DH */
152 u_int min, max, nbits; /* GEX */
153 EC_KEY *ec_client_key; /* ECDH */
154 const EC_GROUP *ec_group; /* ECDH */
155 u_char c25519_client_key[CURVE25519_SIZE]; /* 25519 + KEM */
156 u_char c25519_client_pubkey[CURVE25519_SIZE]; /* 25519 */
157 u_char sntrup4591761_client_key[crypto_kem_sntrup4591761_SECRETKEYBYTES]; /* KEM */
158 struct sshbuf *client_pub;
159};

223void kexc25519_keygen(u_char key[CURVE25519_SIZE], u_char pub[CURVE25519_SIZE])
224 __attribute__((__bounded__(__minbytes__, 1, CURVE25519_SIZE)))
225 __attribute__((__bounded__(__minbytes__, 2, CURVE25519_SIZE)));
226int kexc25519_shared_key(const u_char key[CURVE25519_SIZE],
227 const u_char pub[CURVE25519_SIZE], struct sshbuf *out)
228 __attribute__((__bounded__(__minbytes__, 1, CURVE25519_SIZE)))
229 __attribute__((__bounded__(__minbytes__, 2, CURVE25519_SIZE)));
230int kexc25519_shared_key_ext(const u_char key[CURVE25519_SIZE],
231 const u_char pub[CURVE25519_SIZE], struct sshbuf *out, int)
232 __attribute__((__bounded__(__minbytes__, 1, CURVE25519_SIZE)))
233 __attribute__((__bounded__(__minbytes__, 2, CURVE25519_SIZE)));
